name: Lover hero
description:
During the reign of Vladimir Ilyich he was not afraid to be a liberal. His father abandoned him for his vulgar style and manner of expression, his mother prayed for days for his future. But he wanted to create and paint chiseled Soviet cars. 
And Stepan was not accepted in the Soviet Union. And no one wanted to give him their official car. And Stepan had to survive in his country.
